{"tid":2052582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒指日方將習近平訪日行程推遲至明春後","createTime":"2020-06-05T15:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T02:08:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ee062572291a89f0c65a9620e5647c1ddbd421","tid":2052582,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"日媒指日方將習近平訪日行程推遲至明春後<br />\n05.06.2020 23:20<br />\n日本共同社引述政府消息人士說，日方基本決定暫停協調國家主席習近平，今年國事訪日的相關日程，主要是由於日本保守派反對習近平訪日的聲音升溫，以及中美對立激化。首相官邸和外務省認為，即使新型冠狀病毒疫情趨於平息，習近平訪日環境亦不成熟，行程將推遲到明年春季以後。<br />\n<br />\n外相茂木敏充日前預計習近平將在11月後訪日，但日本防衛相河野太郎就表露要謹慎考慮的想法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1300770&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1300770%26csid%3D261_341&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=93955d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1300770&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7304170d51ef9cc71b8449b3cfc690fbad947a11","tid":2052582,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"日：你做得到下年咪過黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b671402c6ae71cdfa81a664c65bf6fc797a42cd7","tid":2052582,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:54:37.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800baf49cf82b772c79c42e99c0298f00c9035ae","tid":2052582,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"推下又一年，推下又一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}